-- Virgin Blue to Fold V Australia Long-Haul Unit Into Company, Reuters Says
-- Nichola Saminather
-- 2010-06-30T08:27:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/virgin-blue-to-fold-v-australia-long-haul-unit-into-company-reuters-says.html

          
          
                  June 30 (Bloomberg) --Virgin Blue Holdings Ltd. will
integrate the carrier’s long-haul operation V Australia into its
main business, Reuters reported in a story carried on the Sydney
Morning Herald website, citing a memo from Chief Executive
Officer John Borghetti to the airline’s staff.  
 Borghetti will also expand his team of senior executives to
eight from six as part of changes to the company’s management,
according to the report.  
